Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: house tech radio
des: Along the HouseTech Radio journey, we have attracted Underground House and Techno DJs, Producers, Promotors, and most importantly, friends from all over the world with one thing in common, a love of Underground House and Techno music in all its forms. We are also lucky to have established a great team that continues to support the HouseTech spirit by promoting DJs & Producers. The idea of this radio station and growing online community is to provide a professional and fun platform for all DJs to play on and showcase their sounds.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
